    {
      "title": "GitHub - Yannisxm/AirsimSimulation: A maze simulation environment in Unreal Engine for quadrotor. · GitHub",
      "link": "https://github.com/Yannisxm/AirsimSimulation",
      "snippet": "Yannisxm/AirsimSimulation   master Go to file Code Open more actions menu Folders and files Name Name Last commit message Last commit date Latest commit   History 24 Commits 24 Commits Binaries/ Win64 Binaries/ Win64     Config Config     Content Content     Intermediate Intermediate     Plugins Plugins     Saved Saved     Source Source     .gitattributes .gitattributes     .gitignore .gitignore     LICENSE LICENSE     README.md README.md     VehilceAdvanced.sln VehilceAdvanced.sln     VehilceAdvanced.uproject VehilceAdvanced.uproject     View all files Repository files navigation The simulation enviroument based on Airsim is developed to verify the dynamic model and the designed control algorithm for quadrotor.The quadrotor' motion is restrained in a narrow corridor, which represents a much more challenging workspace because any oscillation with the walls may cause the crash of the quadrotor vehicle.The successive desired waypoints are specified on the critical corners of the maze map",
      "date": "2026-05-11 02:48:47"
    },
    {
      "title": "2022世界空中智能博弈大赛",
      "link": "http://cicc-aig.c2.org.cn/index.html",
      "snippet": "2022 世界空中智能博弈大赛(Air Intelligence Game,AIG)是由中国指挥与控制学会主办,以推动人工智能技术在军事领域的创新研究和应用为目的,构建典型空战场景,拓展异构、协同空战的作战样式和作战机理,支撑多种人工智能建模方式,包括且不限于机器学习、强化学习、规则驱动等。大赛针对空中作战等场景设计典型赛题,期望通过本次比赛可以沉淀智能化算法、数据、知识,探索机器决策认知能力,赋能作战指挥决策。 ",
      "date": "2026-04-27 04:06:42"
    },
    {
      "title": "拿到一篇论文,如何查看该论文提交到arXiv上的时间【科研小技巧】_arxiv论文网站-CSDN博客",
      "link": "https://blog.csdn.net/zly19980718/article/details/144571032",
      "snippet": "1､打开arXiv官方网站:https://arxiv.org/｡ 2､在右上角的搜索框输入要检索的文章标题并进行检索,以Understanding Diffusion Models: A Unified Perspective这篇论文为例｡ 3､检索到文章后,可以看到文章标题的正上方有个[Submitted on 25 Aug 2022],表示该文章在2022年8月25日提交到arXiv上的｡ 4､在下载的PDF论文中, 在第一页可以看到有一个 25 Aug 2022,同样表示该论文是在2022年8月25日提交到arXiv上的｡",
      "date": "2024-12-18 22:27:14"
    },
